{"tid":2495172,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都有人話 你講嘅嘢可以套落其他地方","createTime":"2021-04-19T04:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T07:21:18.000Z","uid":394002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c32a38250efce8ba13cebb8e14473815f4595aa","tid":2495172,"uid":394002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"咁代表咩？有邏輯問題？<br />\n求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea5f9d1eaba2a1d584c67047edba1f8fbb0fe0c","tid":2495172,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:49:50.000Z","msg":"講啲嘢模稜兩可？"},{"pid":"84276d512d3807ecbb686bd03487f59da6a50478","tid":2495172,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"too general, not specific"},{"pid":"f9f15029fdd1807a9b341af1ac9677ff4a3a1aae","tid":2495172,"uid":394002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea5f9d1eaba2a1d584c67047edba1f8fbb0fe0c","tid":2495172,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:49:50.000Z","msg":"講啲嘢模稜兩可？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:55:01.000Z","msg":"「我曾經唔想林家謙紅 」       希望佢可以睇到呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aNgCyoV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aNgCyoV</a><br />\n#10 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n非林家謙fans, 介唔介意用呢個例子去解釋一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba25f98e90b634540f10e17bf3e5a4d9ef53025d","tid":2495172,"uid":394002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84276d512d3807ecbb686bd03487f59da6a50478","tid":2495172,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"too general, not specific"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"I thought it&rsquo;s applicable to different areas as long as the statements were reasonable<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c946169896ce63e76a9d640b052a3fbde009baa","tid":2495172,"uid":158886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"如果用《我曾經唔想林家謙紅 》呢個post做例子嘅話，可以從幾個方向去思考。 我地先當原樓主所寫嘅野全部係真嘅，理論上唔會有兩個藝人成名嘅過程係一模一樣嘅，原樓主寫得都算仔細，所以嚴格黎講係無得套落其他人身上嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解#5會認為可以套落去呢？我嘅睇法係因為佢分唔開文章內容同思路兩者之間嘅關係。  佢講得無錯，原樓主的確係怕人性中嘅利欲熏心，但呢個只係佢寫呢段嘢或者有『唔想林家謙紅』呢個念頭背後嘅原因。（思路）     原樓主個post嘅內文並唔係好似#5所形容嘅咁，用一啲好general啲描述就帶過成件事。 佢有提到林家謙一啲比較獨特嘅經歷，而#5就單單抽左樓主『怕人性中嘅利欲熏心。』呢個想法出黎檢視。 呢個例子中，可以套落其他地方嘅係『怕人性中嘅利欲熏心。』呢個心態，而唔係原樓主個post。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者我舉個再簡單啲嘅例子， 例如我話『提子好好味，因為.......下刪10個獨特嘅理由......』其實XX好好味呢個statement係常見到不得了，但係因為我後續提供嘅10個獨特嘅理由，導致提子嘅好味不能套用落其他食物，因為其他食物未必有晒導致我覺得提子好味嘅要素。 所以我成句野並唔可以套落其他地方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTLDR: 要睇個『嘢』係指咩，係個statement定係論點，如果係statement其實無乜所謂，因為實際影響個validity嘅係個論點。 如果係指論點，就要睇有無獨特嘅證據去support。而且兩者必須合併檢視，如果淨係抽晒啲用詞或者句式出黎，咁世界上應該無咩唔可以互相套用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6766e7a65c64f6d6e625919a857e7645224b5c","tid":2495172,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"你比個例子? 如果你講物理定律唔可以套用係其他地方，咁可能係你有問題多。<br />\n如果你講某國法律精神唔可以套用其他地方，咁可能係你岩"},{"pid":"def1639747447757618f6cbd3d23379792e8bac9","tid":2495172,"uid":28730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba25f98e90b634540f10e17bf3e5a4d9ef53025d","tid":2495172,"uid":394002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84276d512d3807ecbb686bd03487f59da6a50478","tid":2495172,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"too general, not specific"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"I thought it&rsquo;s applicable to different areas as long as the statements were reasonable<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"係 但同時會唔會冇咁左啲直接扣題既論述？"},{"pid":"54e7c6d5b05487664a167579e9492c97a3ac4d7f","tid":2495172,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f15029fdd1807a9b341af1ac9677ff4a3a1aae","tid":2495172,"uid":394002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea5f9d1eaba2a1d584c67047edba1f8fbb0fe0c","tid":2495172,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:49:50.000Z","msg":"講啲嘢模稜兩可？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:55:01.000Z","msg":"「我曾經唔想林家謙紅 」       希望佢可以睇到呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aNgCyoV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aNgCyoV</a><br />\n#10 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n非林家謙fans, 介唔介意用呢個例子去解釋一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:16:05.000Z","msg":"MLA同serrini都可以套用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開始鍾意serrini嘅歌已經係好耐以前，仲係佢唱你條茂利放飛機嘅時候，仲係佢YouTube 自彈自唱嘅年代，再到仲可以開concert開到爆場的時候<br />\n<br />\n佢慢慢開始紅，我開始驚<br />\n<br />\n我驚佢紅左會變，紅係要兼顧好多野，會變到好識講野好世界女，兼顧別人的口味和期望，變到冇左本身八婆嘅性格，怕佢為咗唔比人鬧收埋自己，所有野都唔會做多唔會突出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598d5eef212cae58d73988b6f44fc67aa61e011b","tid":2495172,"uid":394002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54e7c6d5b05487664a167579e9492c97a3ac4d7f","tid":2495172,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f15029fdd1807a9b341af1ac9677ff4a3a1aae","tid":2495172,"uid":394002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea5f9d1eaba2a1d584c67047edba1f8fbb0fe0c","tid":2495172,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:49:50.000Z","msg":"講啲嘢模稜兩可？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:55:01.000Z","msg":"「我曾經唔想林家謙紅 」       希望佢可以睇到呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aNgCyoV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aNgCyoV</a><br />\n#10